# Firebase credential files — replace placeholders with real files locally,
# but never commit the real credentials to version control.
# The placeholder template files (google-services.json, GoogleService-Info.plist)
# ARE tracked so developers know what structure is expected.
# To use: copy the real file alongside the placeholder and rename it, or
# replace the placeholder content with real values locally (and keep it out of git).
#
# If you want to track the placeholder but not a real file, use a naming
# convention like google-services.real.json and add that pattern here instead.
#
# Uncomment the lines below once you have replaced the placeholders with real files:
# android/app/google-services.json
# ios/Runner/GoogleService-Info.plist
